This Swift package implements the SPICE vd_agent wire protocol as
described in the public specification published by the SPICE project
at <https://www.spice-space.org/agent-protocol.html>.

The protocol specification documentation is maintained by Red Hat and
the SPICE project. No source code from SPICE reference implementations
(spice-vdagent, spice-gtk, spice-protocol, utmapp/vd_agent) was copied
or derived; every line in this package was written from the
specification text alone.

See docs/SPEC_ATTRIBUTION.md for the detailed chain of custody.
